Define Stock Splitting Parameters

Source: R/StoxBaselineFunctions.R
DefineStockSplittingParameters.Rd

Defines parameters for the stock-splitting analysis in Reca, including parameters for misclassifying when determining stock membership of a specimen.

DefineStockSplittingParameters(
  processData,
  DefinitionMethod = c("ResourceFile", "FunctionParameters"),
  FileName = character(),
  StockNameCC = character(),
  StockNameS = character(),
  ProbabilityType1As1 = numeric(),
  ProbabilityType5As1 = numeric(),
  ProbabilityType2As2 = numeric(),
  ProbabilityType4As2 = numeric(),
  ProbabilityType2As4 = numeric(),
  ProbabilityType4As4 = numeric(),
  ProbabilityType1As5 = numeric(),
  ProbabilityType5As5 = numeric(),
  UseProcessData = F
)

Arguments

processData

data.table() as returned from this function
DefinitionMethod

'ResourceFile' or 'FunctionParameters', see details.
FileName

path to resource file
StockNameCC

Variable for StockSplittingParameters
StockNameS

Variable for StockSplittingParameters
ProbabilityType1As1

Variable for StockSplittingParameters
ProbabilityType5As1

Variable for StockSplittingParameters
ProbabilityType2As2

Variable for StockSplittingParameters
ProbabilityType4As2

Variable for StockSplittingParameters
ProbabilityType2As4

Variable for StockSplittingParameters
ProbabilityType4As4

Variable for StockSplittingParameters
ProbabilityType1As5

Variable for StockSplittingParameters
ProbabilityType5As5

Variable for StockSplittingParameters
UseProcessData

If TRUE, bypasses execution of function and returns existing 'processData'

Value

StockSplittingParameters.

Details

For DefinitionMethod 'ResourceFile', definitions are read from a UTF-8 encoded tab separated file with headers and one row with headers corresponding to column names in StockSplittingParameters. see StockSplittingParameters for further explanation on the coding system.

For DefinitionMethod 'FunctionParameters' defintions are constructed from parameters to this function.

See also

PrepareRecaEstimate for use of stock-splitting parameters in Reca-estimation.
